      "*": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><p>\n<aside role=\"region\" class=\"portable-infobox pi-background pi-border-color pi-theme-Chapter pi-layout-default\">\n<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-item-spacing pi-title pi-secondary-background\" data-source=\"title\">The Great Adventure of Usopp the Man</h2>\n\n<figure class=\"pi-item pi-image\" data-source=\"image\">\n\t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/5/57/Chapter_70.png/revision/latest?cb=20130121040154\" class=\"image image-thumbnail\" title=\"Chapter 70\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/5/57/Chapter_70.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/268?cb=20130121040154\" srcset=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/5/57/Chapter_70.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/268?cb=20130121040154 1x, https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/5/57/Chapter_70.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/536?cb=20130121040154 2x\" class=\"pi-image-thumbnail\" data-relevant=\"1\" alt=\"Chapter 70\" width=\"270\" height=\"190\" data-image-key=\"Chapter_70.png\" data-image-name=\"Chapter 70.png\" />\n\t\t\n\t</a>\n\t\n</figure>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Chapter Info</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"vol\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Volume:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Volume_8\" title=\"Volume 8\">8</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"chapter\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Chapter:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">70</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"jname\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Japanese Title:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">男ウソップ大冒険</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"rname\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Romanized Title:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><i>Otoko Usoppu Daibōken</i></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"ename\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Viz Title:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">The Great Adventure of Usopp the Man</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"page\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Pages:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">21</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"date2\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Release Date:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">January 4, 1999<span class=\"plainlinks\" title=\"Release dates obtained from http&#58;//www.thegrandline.com\"><sup><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.thegrandline.com/odatocLIVE.htm\">[ref]</a></sup></span></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"jump\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">WSJ Issue:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">1999 Issue 6</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"anime\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Anime:</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Episode_31\" title=\"Episode 31\">Episode 31</a> (p. 1, 4-13)<br /><a href=\"/wiki/Episode_32\" title=\"Episode 32\">Episode 32</a> (p. 14-20)<br /></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<table class=\"pi-horizontal-group pi-horizontal-group-no-labels\">\n\t<caption class=\"pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-secondary-background pi-item-spacing\">Chapter Chronology</caption>\n\t\n\t<tbody>\n\t<tr>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\">← <a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_69\" title=\"Chapter 69\">Previous</a></td>\n\t\n\t\t<td class=\"pi-horizontal-group-item pi-data-value pi-font pi-border-color pi-item-spacing\"><a href=\"/wiki/Chapter_71\" title=\"Chapter 71\">Next</a> →</td>\n\t\n\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n<b>Chapter 70</b> is titled \"The Great Adventure of Usopp the Man\".\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Cover_Page\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Cover Page</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Short_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Short Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Long_Summary\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Long Summary</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quick_Reference\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quick Reference</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Chapter_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chapter Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Characters\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Characters</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Author_Comment\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Author Comment</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Trivia\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Trivia</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Site_Navigation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Site Navigation</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Cover_Page\">Cover Page</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_70%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Cover_Page#Color_Spread\" title=\"Cover Page\">Color Spread</a>: The <a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a> as samurai, all dressed in <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kabukimono\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Kabukimono\">Kabukimono</a>-esque clothing and all wielding at least one sword. <a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Luffy</a> in particular is perched on an upside-down wok, holding an <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oil-paper_umbrella\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Oil-paper umbrella\">oil-paper parasol</a> while unsheathing his red-lacquered sword with his teeth.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Short_Summary\">Short Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_70%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Zoro</a> arrives at <a href=\"/wiki/Arlong_Park\" title=\"Arlong Park\">Arlong Park</a>. <a href=\"/wiki/Nojiko\" title=\"Nojiko\">Nojiko</a> is introduced and revealed to be <a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a>'s sister.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Long_Summary\">Long Summary</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_70%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Zoro</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Johnny\" title=\"Johnny\">Johnny</a> arrive in front of <a href=\"/wiki/Arlong_Park\" title=\"Arlong Park\">Arlong Park</a>. In order to prevent Zoro from foolishly attacking the <a href=\"/wiki/Fish-men\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Fish-men\">fish-men</a>, he's tied up by Johnny and Usopp while they search for the <a href=\"/wiki/Going_Merry\" title=\"Going Merry\">Going Merry</a>. They soon found it anchored near a local village. Usopp, who acted bravely once away from Arlong Park, becomes a coward again once he notices three Fish-Men next to the boat. He and Johnny flee into the sea once they have been spotted, leaving Zoro alone and powerless in front of the Fish-Men.\n</p><p>When Usopp and Johnny pull themselves out of the sea, they notice that the village has been completely devastated and postulate it was destroyed by the Fish-Men. They are impressed by the power of these creatures. They find one of the Fish-Men has returned to the village, suspicious of Zoro being alone. While Johnny is able to hide himself, Usopp starts running until he bumps into a kid, <a href=\"/wiki/Chabo\" title=\"Chabo\">Chabo</a>, and a woman, <a href=\"/wiki/Nojiko\" title=\"Nojiko\">Nojiko</a>. When the Fish-Man is about to capture them, Usopp decides to act bravely for once, and tries to defend the two villagers, but is knocked out by Nojiko.\n</p><p>When he wakes up, the three of them are in Nojiko's house, in an orange farm. Nojiko tells them that nobody fights the fish-men because it's suicide. Chabo, a boy from <a href=\"/wiki/Gosa_Village\" title=\"Gosa Village\">Gosa Village</a>, whose father has been killed, understands this, and returns to his mother rather than seeking revenge.\n</p><p>Usopp understands that Nojiko's intentions are not bad, and tells her that he is looking for <a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a>. Nojiko then tells Usopp that Nami and her are adopted sisters, and that Nami is a member of <a href=\"/wiki/Arlong_Pirates\" title=\"Arlong Pirates\">Arlong Pirates</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quick_Reference\">Quick Reference</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_70%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapter_Notes\">Chapter Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_70%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D5&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Zoro</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a>, and <a href=\"/wiki/Johnny\" title=\"Johnny\">Johnny</a> arrive at <a href=\"/wiki/Cocoyasi_Village\" title=\"Cocoyasi Village\">Cocoyasi Village</a>, the site of <a href=\"/wiki/Arlong_Park\" title=\"Arlong Park\">Arlong Park</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Nojiko\" title=\"Nojiko\">Nojiko</a> is introduced, and reveals that she and <a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a> are stepsisters.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_70%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D6&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table class=\"CharTable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/Pirate\" title=\"Pirate\">Pirates</a>\n</th>\n<th>Citizens\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/Bounty_Hunter\" title=\"Bounty Hunter\">Bounty Hunters</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Monkey_D._Luffy\" title=\"Monkey D. Luffy\">Monkey D. Luffy</a> <i>(cover)</i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Roronoa_Zoro\" title=\"Roronoa Zoro\">Roronoa Zoro</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a> <i>(cover)</i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Usopp\" title=\"Usopp\">Usopp</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Sanji\" title=\"Sanji\">Sanji</a> <i>(cover)</i></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Arlong_Pirates\" title=\"Arlong Pirates\">Arlong Pirates</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Arlong\" title=\"Arlong\">Arlong</a> <i>(image)</i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Hatchan\" title=\"Hatchan\">Hatchan</a> <i>(shadowed)</i></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Nami\" title=\"Nami\">Nami</a> <i>(image)</i></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Gosa_Village\" title=\"Gosa Village\">Gosa Village</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Chabo\" title=\"Chabo\">Chabo</a></li></ul>\n<hr />\n<dl><dt><a href=\"/wiki/Cocoyasi_Village\" title=\"Cocoyasi Village\">Cocoyasi Village</a></dt></dl>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Nojiko\" title=\"Nojiko\">Nojiko</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Johnny\" title=\"Johnny\">Johnny</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Author_Comment\">Author Comment</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_70%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D7&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><br />\n</p><table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: auto; text-align: center; width:50%\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">Author Comment</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:90%\"><div class=\"tabber wds-tabber\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__wrapper with-bottom-border\"><ul class=\"wds-tabs\"><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab wds-is-current\" data-hash=\"Translation\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Translation</a></div></li><li class=\"wds-tabs__tab\" data-hash=\"Original\"><div class=\"wds-tabs__tab-label\"><a href=\"#\">Original</a></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\"><p><br />\nHappy New Year I wanted to try using a large font just once. But seriously it's just like, definitely a happy time n'stuff.</p></div><div class=\"wds-tab__content\"><p><br />\n明けましておめでとう 一度こういうでかい文字を入れてみたかった。しかしあれですねめでたいっすねー</p></div></div>—<a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\">Eiichiro Oda</a></td><td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Eiichiro_Oda\" title=\"Eiichiro Oda\"><img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/onepiece/images/a/ad/Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/100?cb=20230801133230\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Eiichiro Oda WSJ Avatar.png\" data-image-key=\"Eiichiro_Oda_WSJ_Avatar.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"><i>English translation by <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.thegrandline.com/odatocLIVE.htm\">Greg Werner</a>. For comprehensive translation credits, see <a href=\"/wiki/List_of_WSJ_Author_Comments#Translation_Credits\" title=\"List of WSJ Author Comments\">here</a>.</i></td></tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_70%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D8&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>In the chapter's initial publishing in <a href=\"/wiki/Shonen_Jump\" title=\"Shonen Jump\"><i>Weekly Shonen Jump</i></a>, the first page was printed in full color.</li>\n<li>Although Nami currently is with <a href=\"/wiki/Arlong_Pirates\" title=\"Arlong Pirates\">Arlong's crew</a>, she appears on the story as one of the <a href=\"/wiki/Straw_Hat_Pirates\" title=\"Straw Hat Pirates\">Straw Hat Pirates</a>.</li>\n<li>This is the first chapter where <a href=\"/wiki/Luffy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Luffy\">Luffy</a> only appears on the cover.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Site_Navigation\">Site Navigation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fonepiece.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FChapter_70%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D9&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"toccolours\" style=\"margin:auto; text-